    <title>MVP System slight rework</title>
    <link>https://fol-archive.netlify.app/t/mvp-system-slight-rework/72309</link>
    <description>
First, in order for this work without people swimming in gold like crazy, just slightly nerf the rewards values.
To make people more likely to vote, give extra gold reward if everyone on the game to the time the MVP screen appears has voted three people. Give also extra gold for those who voted on someone that got Gold Star, this will prevent most meme votes as people will likely chose who indeed played well (so they get that sweet extra gold)</description>
    
